verbose_text: SDF-1 is expressed in synovial epithelial cells and it has been reported that persistent induction of CXCR4 by stromal derived factors, such as TGF-beta led to SDF-1 mediated accumulation of CD4 T cells within the rheumatoid joint XREF_BIBR.
evidence: CXCR4 by stromal derived factors, such as TGF-beta led to SDF-1 mediated accumulation of CD4
